'''Private Security and Intelligence Servive''' is a German-American [[private military company]] founded in 1999 by [[Torsten Grunert]] and [[Richard Gates]].

Based in Germany ([[Cologne]]) and in the US ([[Towson, Maryland|Towson]]), PSIS operates two secret facilities.

